{% comment %}MAGMA ENERGY — Testimonials{% endcomment %}

<style>
  .magma-testi {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: 100px 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .magma-testi__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .magma-testi__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .magma-testi__card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 40px 36px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .magma-testi__card:hover {
    background: var(--color-surface-2);
  }

  .magma-testi__stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    color: var(--color-energy);
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .magma-testi__quote {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    flex: 1;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .magma-testi__quote::before {
    content: '"';
    font-family: var(--font-headline);
    font-size: 48px;
    line-height: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.4;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .magma-testi__author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .magma-testi__avatar {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-surface-2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 196, 180, 0.3);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-headline);
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .magma-testi__name {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .magma-testi__role {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .magma-testi {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }

    .magma-testi__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="magma-testi">
  <div class="magma-container">
    <div class="magma-testi__header">
      <div class="magma-eyebrow magma-animate">Lo Que Dicen</div>
      <h2 class="magma-h2 magma-animate">RESULTADOS<br><span style="color:var(--color-accent)">REALES</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="magma-testi__grid">
      <div class="magma-testi__card magma-animate">
        <div class="magma-testi__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="magma-testi__quote">
          Lo uso antes del gym y la diferencia es brutal. Energía limpia, sin el nerviosismo que me da el café.
        </p>
        <div class="magma-testi__author">
          <div class="magma-testi__avatar">M</div>
          <div>
            <div class="magma-testi__name">Matías R.</div>
            <div class="magma-testi__role">Atleta · Buenos Aires</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="magma-testi__card magma-animate">
        <div class="magma-testi__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="magma-testi__quote">
          Perfecto para estudiar. No tengo que interrumpir nada, lo pongo y me concentro. Sin calorías encima.
        </p>
        <div class="magma-testi__author">
          <div class="magma-testi__avatar">V</div>
          <div>
            <div class="magma-testi__name">Valentina G.</div>
            <div class="magma-testi__role">Estudiante universitaria</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="magma-testi__card magma-animate">
        <div class="magma-testi__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="magma-testi__quote">
          Me lo llevé de viaje y fue un game changer. No ocupa lugar, no se derrama y funciona igual que siempre.
        </p>
        <div class="magma-testi__author">
          <div class="magma-testi__avatar">S</div>
          <div>
            <div class="magma-testi__name">Santiago L.</div>
            <div class="magma-testi__role">Emprendedor · Córdoba</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "MAGMA — Testimonials",
  "tag": "section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "MAGMA — Testimonials"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
